# Phase 21: SetList Panel Icon Layout & Bottom Toolbar Redesign

This phase focuses on replacing the existing SetList toolbar with a more professional, high-density segmented control layout consisting of two horizontal icon bars. It also introduces new functionality like "Clear All", "Favorite marking", and "Refresh".

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The new button bars are strictly 20px high each, which is quite small for touch targets but fits the requested high-density "professional" look.
> Icons will be sized approximately 14-16px to fit comfortably.

> [!NOTE]
> The "Engraved" look will be achieved using a monochrome icon color with a subtle drop shadow or specific HSL color selection to simulate depth on the gradient background.

